posts.title: MAGA Monday Actions
posts.content:
Hello fellow Pedes.

We're in the 4th quarter of this game and it is up to us to prevent this game from going into unnecessary overtime. This means that we seek out actionable steps that all of us can do to ensure that a Trump-Vance victory is Too Big to Rig in November.

Our first MAGA Monday Action, or MMA, is to make contact with people you know that are open to voting for Trump and commit to driving them to the polls in November.

  1. Reach out to at least 7 individuals open to voting for Trump by week's end. Aim for 5 commitments, but any number is a win.

  2. Encourage those you find already committed for Trump to recruit others.

  3. Schedule a time to meet with anyone on the fence to discuss the benefits of supporting Trump vs. extending our decline under Harris.

  4. Provide a ride to the poll. Schedule and commit in advance. Sometimes it's just just a matter bringing them to the polls.

  5. Assist in driving other supporters to the polls on Election Day. One extra ride can make a difference.

While all of the above activities can be done on their own you can increase your effectiveness by signing up to volunteer at https://trumpforce47.com

As always verify that you're registered and know where to vote: https://www.usa.gov/state-election-office

Sign-up to be a Poll-Worker https://patriots.win/p/17txRDHXhQ/maga-pollworker-megathread-v2/

Sign up to be a Poll-Watcher: https://www.protectthevote.com/volunteer/

Fight election fraud by reporting suspicious activities via True the Vote's Vote Alert App https://www.votealert.org
